text: Bellinzona is a district of the canton of Ticino in Switzerland. == Circles and municipalities == * circle of Bellinzona: Bellinzona, Arbedo-Castione, Lumino; * circle of the Ticino: Monte Carasso, Gudo, Sementina, Gorduno, Gnosca, Preonzo, Moleno; * circle of Giubiasco: Giubiasco, Pianezzo, Sant'Antonio, Camorino, Sant'Antonino, Cadenazzo, Medeglia, Isone.
